PETITION INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS

1. Install the necessary database tables:

$ mysql -p -u USER DBNAME < inc/app/petition/install/install-mysql.sql
(enter password when prompted)

2. Copy the petition collection definition into the cms app:

$ cd /PATH/TO/SITELLITE
$ cp -R inc/app/petition/install/petition.php inc/app/cms/conf/collections/

3. Configure the application settings in the file
inc/app/petition/conf/properties.php

4. Create a new petition by logging into Sitellite and going to
Control Panel > Content > Petitions

5. Link to /index/petition-app or use the box chooser to embed the petition
into a web page.
